item.title: New Lv.2 Wasteland Pictures
item.content:encoded:
The first four leveling allies (Flute, Sticky, The Twins, and Tubby) all have new lvl. 2 pictures. I uploaded them to their appropriate level two pages, and if a mod could change the names of the old ones to something else and the new ones to the previous names, all places using the pictures in the wiki will be updated.

Note: Both the lvl 1 and 2 pages of Flutie had been changed, and they will both need to be reverted once the new picture has the correct name.
